metadata.description:
You are cordially invited to a public AMA hosted by The Noun Square on Twitter, to answer any and all questions you may have about the "This is Nouns" special edition drop, or about Nouns DAO more generally. 

Thursday January 5/2023 @ 2PM PST/ 5PM EST / 10PM UTC.

See you there, at the Square! 

RSVP @ https://tinyurl.com/thisisnouns
